        I am a defensive specialist and security researcher focused on Windows internals, telemetry, and AI security.
        I enjoy understanding adversarial tradecraft to find ways to identify, expose, and prevent that tradecraft - approaching
        offensive techniques through a defender's lens. This blog is where I showcase my research, as well as share the methodology
        behind the research.
      </p>
      <p>
        Find me on <a href="https://github.com/jonny-jhnson">GitHub</a> · <a href="https://x.com/JonnyJohnson_">X</a>.
      </p>
